lyTime":"2017-11-17T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係認字特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認字唔認人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07de2bc653868f11286bd4e20c0e7a95f7ddbff","tid":471073,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:50:49.000Z","msg":"人稱阿水的兒童節目主持人司徒瑞祈，最近離巢開小食店做老闆，主打小食、意粉和特飲，當中不少自家制，包括黑糖冬瓜茶、素菜春卷、一口西多等。阿水唔止每日駐場招呼街坊，連採購食材、煮食也一手包辦，連近日8號風球、10號風球都照開門，等附近居民打風都有嘢食，如此拼搏，背後原來是個追夢故事。<br />\n<br />\n出道十年決心追夢開食店<br />\n講起阿水司徒瑞祈，可能你會想起游泳港隊、中學時睇過的青春愛情劇《赤沙印記@四葉草2》，甚至兒童節目《放學ICU》。為何突然唔做藝人，開店做生意？阿水說：「開小食店是自己多年來的夢想，自己也喜歡煮食，閒時煮給朋友吃，也會hashtag阿水廚房。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/xngk6yq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2Fxngk6yq.html&d=m%2Fae%2Fr5VMBUDgVt2IB%2BLYLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=3e776bc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/xngk6yq.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf27fd851b6134cb82addccd46763feb8d54c5b4","tid":471073,"uid":157734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"咁近排做緊咩？仲有冇係電視上出現？"},{"pid":"468962b771f57af2c7f396172456e402d7a0a6d9","tid":471073,"uid":147770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"我想知dickson哥哥係咪gay"},{"pid":"eefa9b8166d1a79f5741c593ae9395d1c6d0626c","tid":471073,"uid":58254,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:56:15.000Z","msg":"點睇你既同行，笑波子？"},{"pid":"96e2c83d60eccb65c6d3e33d7d991f62bad45158","tid":471073,"uid":120317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇你既同行，笑波子？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm